KixMail is a simple, light-weight and fast email client for the Unix Desktop.

Installation
============
See the 'INSTALL' file for installation instructions.

Hacking
=======
See the 'HACKING' file for information about hacking on kixMail.

Mailing List
============


Reporting Bugs
==============

For Debug logs, run kixmail as follows:

 $ G_MESSAGES_DEBUG=all KIXMAIL_DEBUG=all ./kixmail

If you are building kixmail from source and installing in a non-standard directory,
Then add the path of 'share' to XDG_DATA_DIRS. This will fix the errors thrown by
gsettings.